{"type": "article", "id": 15748, "title": "Chanel 秀场变机场，以及，H&M亚洲最大旗舰店进驻香港｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2015-10-08T09:41:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1936, "name": "香水"}, {"id": 1898, "name": "时装周"}, {"id": 2862, "name": "旗舰店"}, {"id": 1743, "name": "裁员"}, {"id": 992, "name": "Chanel"}, {"id": 1060, "name": "H&M"}, {"id": 1782, "name": "Coach"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607144445DJWSI3ojZ6He28Cz.png", "contents": "\n\n<h3>\r\n\t一些重要的新闻：\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/C-A-Foundation-unveils-partnership-with-WWF-India,580077.html#.VhWy4nhVfBI\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>C&amp;A 基金会宣布与印度 WWF 合作</strong></a>｜为保护印度生物多样性以及农民生计，C&amp;A 基金会本周宣布与印度世界野生动物基金会（WWF）携手推出一个致力于帮助 6000 农民获得有机棉认证的的项目，预计 2018 年底实现。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://popbee.cn/fashion/hm-cwb-flagship/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>H&amp;M 亚洲最大旗舰店进驻香港铜锣湾</strong></a>｜H&amp;M 宣布全亚洲最大旗舰店将于 10 月 30 日于铜锣湾 Fashion Walk开幕，面积达 4.7 万平方英尺，H&amp;M Home 也将首次亮相于香港。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.nofashion.cn/a/1443773811847.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Escada 大幅裁员 200 人</strong></a>｜德国时尚品牌 Escada 宣布裁员 200 人，将占集团 2000 人的 10%，其中 150 人为德总部人员，此次裁员是该公司管理混乱不断更换首席执行官后的又一“灾难性”表现。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.nofashion.cn/a/1444059752141.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Hermès 版 Apple Watch 中国开卖</strong></a>｜9 月 10 日苹果推出的爱马仕版 Apple Watch 本周正式在中国大陆市场上市，售价在 8688 至 11888 元人名币。外包装并非苹果常见的白色，而是采用 Hermès 经典的橘色，印有两大品牌的 logo。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t一些值得一看的：\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2015/10/05/coach-gary-baseman-wild-beast-collection/#slide-8\" target=\"_blank\"><span></span>Coach 与艺术家 Gary Baseman 合作名为 “Wild Beast” 的豹纹系列：</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2015/10/05/coach-gary-baseman-wild-beast-collection/#slide-8\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607144433b2jCyNfiaOmtWehs.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56471816\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2015/10/05/coach-gary-baseman-wild-beast-collection/#slide-8\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607144433CY25MHFRxALergWd.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56471816\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2015/10/05/coach-gary-baseman-wild-beast-collection/#slide-8\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607144434uaSURTVeMZOql1x9.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56471816\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2015/10/05/coach-gary-baseman-wild-beast-collection/#slide-8\" target=\"_blank\"><span> </span> </a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2015/10/05/coach-gary-baseman-wild-beast-collection/#slide-8\" target=\"_blank\"><span> </span> </a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t美国时尚设计师品牌 <a href=\"http://popbee.cn/beauty/perfumes/jill-stuart-crystal-bloom-snow/\" target=\"_blank\">Jill Stuart  又推出一款香水</a>，以冬季为主题，水晶花搭配银色雕花瓶盖。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607144434yXu1q2TfYUAZtwPa.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71172962\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://popbee.cn/celebrities/gigi-hadid-elle-nov2015/\" target=\"_blank\">超模 Gigi Hadid 为<em> Elle </em>十一月号杂志拍摄一组时尚大片</a>，红唇和俏皮露腰装各种风格轻松驾驭。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607144435Bhn0vVO5HoeAKIEG.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607144436d970RZfvFbzpGsUN.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span><strong>这里是一些巴黎时装周值得一看的品牌走秀：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t继超市之后，Chanel 将秀场变成了机场的模样，模特们俨然最时尚的职业女性或是乘务人员等，随身的登机包和行李箱也足够引人注目。时尚圈最会做仪式感的品牌，非香奈儿莫属。\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607144436NEr4Ibsw9HifCYAD.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.49259259\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607144436OCNMGTBzEwf8A97q.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607144437iK7ExfBUjR5unp1F.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66612903\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607144437YgDv2Ue4aGtFQ8WZ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607144438UXjhoMPEVvc0SG9Y.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607144438dxCBOLlUsE64f0hF.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607144439fTC4PZNE1tDKweL6.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\tLouis Vuitton 2016 年春夏成衣系列：<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607144439jzlGBmDrcvRW80CP.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.00092593\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\tValentino <span style=\"text-align:left;\">2016 年春夏成衣系列：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071444408Oyr4SR590mpFDqw.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"2.24722222\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\tMoncler Gamme Rouge <span style=\"text-align:left;\">2016 年春夏成衣系列：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607144441u1ja7AKbrqeHtL6p.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"2.2448037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\tHermes<span style=\"text-align:left;\"> </span><span style=\"text-align:left;\">2016 年春夏成衣系列：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060714444281xSiME5bOuDekjR.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"2.2448037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\tSaint Laurent 2016 年春夏成衣系列：\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607144442WZ6OaPyuEKe2mVXp.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"2.2448037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:left;\">Paul &amp; Joe </span><span style=\"text-align:left;\">2016 年春夏成衣系列：</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607144443oXU7LS2uv9iJpYxk.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"2.2448037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:left;\">Miu Miu </span><span style=\"text-align:left;\">2016 年春夏成衣系列：</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607144444sEuKtWlMfeB9QYg2.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"2.2448037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}